title: AC-DC - 1977-01-07 City Hall Hobart - RIP Malcolm Young
description: Such a sad occasion to share this recording, RIP Malcolm Young (64). For some excellent rare AC/DC video's look in the music video section on TPB. Here is a great performance by AC/DC, live in Hobart. Artwork incl. Please enjoy, share with friends and PLEASE seed for a while, i need your help. Same for the hundreds of other uploads i did and that are still well seeded, do not hit and run but leave your computer running for a while. Oh, and be kind, download maximum 2 or 3 of my uploads at the same time, not 10 or 20 simultanuously... =========================================================================== AC / DC January 7 TH 1977---Hobart Tasmania A Giant Dose of Rock n Roll (Silver Bootleg) Sounds like a Radio or Tv Source with SBD and Venue Microphones 9-/10 This is a really asskicking performance....amazing! 01 Intro (Love Song) Dirty Deeds Done Dirt Cheap 02 She s Got Balls 03 Problem Child 04 Live Wire 05 The Jack 06 Jailbreak 07 TNT 08 Can I Sit Next To You Girl 09 High Voltage 10 Baby Please Dont Go 11 Rocker https://imgur.com/4rnc17k https://imgur.com/kBW5DfR
